    "abstract": "<jats:p>The objective of this research is to demonstrate a mathematical technique to analyze the Covid-19 outbreak, particularly with respect to Malaysia. The technique is able to accommodate scarcity, quantity, and availability of the data set. The obtained results can offer descriptive insight for reflecting and strategizing actions in combating the pandemic.</jats:p>",
